Class TutorialCubeSide

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.fhooe.mcm.it.adid.model.cube.TutorialCubeSide

extends Object
    Class that represents a side of a cube in the TutorialActivity and holds infos where the other sides of the cube a relative to the current front side.
